/div></div><div class="innerbox"><a href="story/most-girls-in-india-drop-out-of-schools-owing-to-fear-of-being-sexually-harassed/1/532944.html">Girls in India drop out of schools owing to fear of being sexually harassed</a><p>This short video talks about the problems that almost every girl faces while on her way to the school and how it harms their basic rights. <br/></p><div class="clear"></div></div></div></div><div class="divclear"></div><div class="boxcont"><div class="box"><h2><a href="section/343/1/fyi.html" target="_blank">FYI</a></h2><div class="posrel"><a href="story/student-suspended-for-speaking-up-against-gender-bias-in-keralas-farooq-college/1/514634.html" title="Student suspended for speaking up against gender bias in Kerala's Farooq college"><img src="http://itgd-mum-dev-static.s3.amazonaws.com/media/others/mediaintoday/indiatoday/lazyload-grey.gif" data-original="http://itgd-mum-dev-static.s3.amazonaws.com/media/others/mediaintoday/indiatoday/images/stories/farooq---storysize_305_110315103832.jpg" alt="Protest poster" title="Protest poster" border="0"/></a><div class="share-story"><div class="share-icon" url="story/student-suspended-for-speaking-up-against-gender-bias-in-keralas-farooq-college/1/514634.html" ctitle="Student suspended for speaking up against gender bias in Kerala's Farooq college"><span class="sharetext"> SHARE </span></div><ul id="514634" style="border:none"></ul></div></div><div class="innerbox"><a href="story/student-suspended-for-speaking-up-against-gender-bias-in-keralas-farooq-college/1/514634.html">Student suspended for speaking up against gender bias in Kerala's Farooq college</a><p>Boys and girls sitting together on a bench doesn't suit the culture of Farooq college in Kozhikode. A student who stood up against it has been suspended.&nbsp; </p><div class="clear"></div></div></div></div><div class="divclear"></div><div class="boxcont"><div class="box"><h2><a href="section/343/1/fyi.html" target="_blank">FYI</a></h2><div class="posrel"><a href="story/watch-why-we-need-to-break-away-from-the-shackles-of-gender-inequality/1/506952.html" title="Watch: Why we need to break away from the shackles of gender inequality"><img src="http://itgd-mum-dev-static.s3.amazonaws.com/media/others/mediaintoday/indiatoday/lazyload-grey.gif" data-original="http://itgd-mum-dev-static.s3.amazonaws.com/media/others/mediaintoday/indiatoday/images/stories/gender-story_305_102515064154.jpg" alt="" title="" border="0"/></a><div class="share-story"><div class="share-icon" url="story/watch-why-we-need-to-break-away-from-the-shackles-of-gender-inequality/1/506952.html" ctitle="Watch: Why we need to break away from the shackles of gender inequality"><span class="sharetext"> SHARE </span></div><ul id="506952" style="border:none"></ul></div></div><div class="innerbox"><a href="story/watch-why-we-need-to-break-away-from-the-shackles-of-gender-inequality/1/506952.html">Watch: Why we need to break away from the shackles of gender inequality</a><p>Video created by NGO Oxfam India explains why it is high time that we moved towards ending gender based inequality in India.&nbsp; </p><div class="clear"></div></div></div></div><div class="divclear"></div><div class="boxcont"><div class="box"><h2><a href="section/343/1/fyi.html" target="_blank">FYI</a></h2><div class="posrel"><a href="story/16-unnecessarily-gendered-products-that-are-not-only-stupid-but-hilarious/1/485514.html" title="16 unnecessarily gendered products that are not only stupid but hilarious"><img src="http://itgd-mum-dev-static.s3.amazonaws.com/media/others/mediaintoday/indiatoday/lazyload-grey.gif" data-original="http://itgd-mum-dev-static.s3.amazonaws.com/media/others/mediaintoday/indiatoday/images/stories/story-size_305_092915115112.jpg" alt="Unnecessarily gendered products" title="Unnecessarily gendered products" border="0"/></a><div class="share-story"><div class="share-icon" url="story/16-unnecessarily-gendered-products-that-are-not-only-stupid-but-hilarious/1/485514.html" ctitle="16 unnecessarily gendered products that are not only stupid but hilarious"><span class="sharetext"> SHARE </span></div><ul id="485514" style="border:none"></ul></div></div><div class="innerbox"><a href="story/16-unnecessarily-gendered-products-that-are-not-only-stupid-but-hilarious/1/485514.html">16 unnecessarily gendered products that are not only stupid but hilarious</a><p>Gendered products have filled the markets and we are consuming them without thinking much.</p><div class="clear"></div></div></div></div><div class="divclear"></div></div></div><div class="clear"></div></div><div class="strwapper"><div id="rightpanel"><style>.gwd-pagedeck &gt; .gwd-page{ position:relative!important;}</style><div id="right-section"><div class="scorecardpublish" id="floatingColumn"><div id="rosRightColumn"><div class="right-ad rt-colum"><script language="JavaScript">
